      "content": "professional help won't fix the fact that the person i was is gone. that person was built on this work. without the research, without the truth... there's just this empty shell that's been pretending to be someone important. it feels like i'm just a ghost haunting a life that doesn't belong to me anymore. i don't see the point in trying to find a 'new' version of myself when the real one is just... deleted.",
